-- London Firefighters Tackle Fire at Metal Recycling Yard
-- B y   P e t e r   W o o d i f i e l d
-- 2012-04-24T15:39:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/london-firefighters-tackle-fire-at-metal-recycling-yard.html
London firefighters are tackling a
fire in a metal recycling yard in Willesden in the northwest of
the U.K. capital.  Thirty firefighters and six fire engines are attending the
blaze on Scrubs Lane, the  London Fire Brigade   said  on its
Twitter page. There are no reports of local residents being
evacuated, spokesman Martin Simpson said in a telephone
interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Woodifield in Edinburgh at 
